Could someone help us? This season we planned to use the IMU ADIS16448(we have had it for a while), we just updated our FRC project to the new Wpilib 2022, but we are getting an error of incompatibility with the ADIS16448 API, checking the GitHub project documentation we noticed that the API hasn’t been updated since 2020.

Could someone help us?

  1. They have added ADIS API into the WPILib. So you can do that for the API. https://github.com/wpilibsuite/allwpilib/pull/3777

  2. The RIO autoSPI problem won’t be resolved until 1-2 more weeks it sounds like, so you won’t be able to run with it yet, is my current understanding.
